L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#C4705A\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"rv-text\">\"Got the bundle as a gift and she cried happy tears. Came neatly packaged, looked beautiful. Will 100% be buying for every birthday from now on.\"</p>\n      <div class=\"rv-foot\">\n        <div class=\"rv-avatar\">L</div>\n        <div><p class=\"rv-name\">Lara M.</p><p class=\"rv-loc\">Jounieh</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rv rv-lav\">\n      <span class=\"rv-book\">Self Care</span>\n      <div class=\"rv-stars\" aria-label=\"5 stars\">\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#6B5BA6\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#6B5BA6\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#6B5BA6\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#6B5BA6\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#6B5BA6\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"rv-text\">\"I bought this for myself and ended up ordering 3 more for friends. The Self Care one is genuinely therapeutic. I colour for 30 mins before bed every night now.\"</p>\n      <div class=\"rv-foot\">\n        <div class=\"rv-avatar\">R</div>\n        <div><p class=\"rv-name\">Rima T.</p><p class=\"rv-loc\">Baabda</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rv rv-sun\">\n      <span class=\"rv-book\">Cozy Cats</span>\n      <div class=\"rv-stars\" aria-label=\"5 stars\">\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#A0720A\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#A0720A\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#A0720A\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#A0720A\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#A0720A\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"rv-text\">\"I'm a huge cat person and this book is everything. Detailed but not stressful to color. Quality is honestly better than I expected for the price.\"</p>\n      <div class=\"rv-foot\">\n        <div class=\"rv-avatar\">N</div>\n        <div><p class=\"rv-name\">Nour A.</p><p class=\"rv-loc\">Achrafieh</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rv rv-sage\">\n      <span class=\"rv-book\">Spooky Cutie</span>\n      <div class=\"rv-stars\" aria-label=\"5 stars\">\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#3D6B4F\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#3D6B4F\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#3D6B4F\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#3D6B4F\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#3D6B4F\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"rv-text\">\"Didn't know what to expect but it's actually so fun. The spooky illustrations are cute not scary. Great quality paper too — my markers didn't bleed at all.\"</p>\n      <div class=\"rv-foot\">\n        <div class=\"rv-avatar\">M</div>\n        <div><p class=\"rv-name\">Maya H.</p><p class=\"rv-loc\">Tripoli</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"rv rv-blush\">\n      <span class=\"rv-book\">Little Cuddles</span>\n      <div class=\"rv-stars\" aria-label=\"5 stars\">\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#C4705A\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#C4705A\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#C4705A\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#C4705A\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n        <svg class=\"rv-star\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#C4705A\"><path d=\"M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z\"/></svg>\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"rv-text\">\"Bought Little Cuddles as a gift. She messaged me the same night saying she couldn't put it down. The packaging was clean and it arrived way faster than I expected.\"</p>\n      <div class=\"rv-foot\">\n        <div class=\"rv-avatar\">D</div>\n        <div><p class=\"rv-name\">Dana R.</p><p class=\"rv-loc\">Sidon</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<!-- ════════════════════════════════\n     GUARANTEES SECTION\n════════════════════════════════ -->\n<section class=\"sec fade-in\">\n  <p class=\"eyebrow\">Before you checkout</p>\n  <h2 class=\"sec-title\">Why thousands in Lebanon shop here.</h2>\n  <p class=\"sec-sub\">No fine print. No surprises. Just good books and a smooth experience.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"g-grid\">\n    <div class=\"gc gc-ink\">\n      <div class=\"gc-icon\">🚚</div>\n      <p class=\"gc-title\">Free delivery on orders above $34</p>\n      <p class=\"gc-body\">Add 2 books or grab the bundle and your shipping is on us. Automatically applied at checkout — no code needed.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"gc gc-sage\">\n      <div class=\"gc-icon\">📍</div>\n      <p class=\"gc-title\">Ships from Lebanon, fast</p>\n      <p class=\"gc-body\">We're local. No customs, no international delays, no \"could take 3–5 weeks.\" Your order moves quickly.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"gc gc-blush\">\n      <div class=\"gc-icon\">📄</div>\n      <p class=\"gc-title\">Thick pages, zero bleed</p>\n      <p class=\"gc-body\">Every book is printed on quality paper that holds up to markers, pencils, and pens. We stand behind what we sell.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"gc gc-lav\">\n      <div class=\"gc-icon\">🎁</div>\n      <p class=\"gc-title\">Arrives gift-ready</p>\n      <p class=\"gc-body\">No extra wrapping needed. Every order comes neat and presentable — perfect to hand over straight from the bag.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"gc gc-sun\">\n      <div class=\"gc-icon\">🤝</div>\n      <p class=\"gc-title\">Something wrong? We fix it</p>\n      <p class=\"gc-body\">If your order arrives damaged or isn't what you expected, reach out and we'll make it right. Simple as that.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<script>\nconst els = document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in');\nif('IntersectionObserver' in window){\n  const obs = new IntersectionObserver(entries=>{\n    entries.forEach(e=>{if(e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('visible');});\n  },{threshold:0.1});\n  els.forEach(el=>obs.observe(el));\n} else {\n  els.forEach(el=>el.classList.add('visible'));\n}\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>",
        "text_alignment": "center"
      }
    }
